=============================================\\nFinished generating 'org.apache.maven.doxia.doxia-module-apt_tests-tests' in 12.7s.\\n\\nThe build process encountered 3 warnings.\\n\\n[native-image-plugin] Native Image written to: /home/vjovanov/c/forge/forge10/graalvm-reachability-metadata/forge/local_repositories/forge_worktrees/7030-70fb287b/tests/src/org.apache.maven.doxia/doxia-module-apt/1.1/build/native/nativeTestCompile\\n\\n> Task :nativeTest\\n[junit-platform-native] WARNING: -djunit.platform.listeners.uid.tracking.output.dir not specified, trying to find test-ids on default Gradle/Maven locations. As this is a fallback mode, it could take a while. This should only happen if you are running tests executable manually and you didn't pass uid output directory with -djunit.platform.listeners.uid.tracking.output.dir=<path>.\\n[junit-platform-native] WARNING: Using test-ids from default Gradle project location:/home/vjovanov/c/forge/forge10/graalvm-reachability-metadata/forge/local_repositories/forge_worktrees/7030-70fb287b/tests/src/org.apache.maven.doxia/doxia-module-apt/1.1/build/test-results/test/testlist\\n[junit-platform-native] Running in 'test listener' mode using files matching pattern [junit-platform-unique-ids*] found in folder [/home/vjovanov/c/forge/forge10/graalvm-reachability-metadata/forge/local_repositories/forge_worktrees/7030-70fb287b/tests/src/org.apache.maven.doxia/doxia-module-apt/1.1/build/test-results/test/testlist] and its subfolders.\\nJUnit Platform on Native Image - report\\n----------------------------------------\\n\\norg_apache_maven_doxia.doxia_module_apt.Doxia_module_aptTest > aptSinkWritesAptMarkupAndEscapesText() SUCCESSFUL\\n\\norg_apache_maven_doxia.doxia_module_apt.Doxia_module_aptTest > parserEmitsStructuredEventsForRichAptDocument() SUCCESSFUL\\n\\norg_apache_maven_doxia.doxia_module_apt.Doxia_module_aptTest > parserEmitsNestedNumberedListsWithExplicitNumberingStyles() SUCCESSFUL\\n\\norg_apache_maven_doxia.doxia_module_ap